You watch over them all.


121
00:08:36.480 --> 00:08:39.650
- In Jesus name, Amen.
- Amen.


122
00:08:40.484 --> 00:08:42.052
All right, little man.

123
00:08:43.354 --> 00:08:44.621
Get you some rest.

124
00:08:44.755 --> 00:08:46.857
Morning comes early
for cowboys.


