Know that we... love you,


980
01:02:24.107 --> 01:02:27.778
and hold you in our hearts
and pray for you every day.


981
01:02:28.680 --> 01:02:30.847
<i>We love you more than</i>
<i>you can know.</i>


982
01:02:30.981 --> 01:02:33.217
Forever and always.

983
01:02:36.887 --> 01:02:39.790
I love--
I love my people, and...


984
01:02:41.659 --> 01:02:43.393
I'll communicate
as I'm able to.


985
01:02:45.762 --> 01:02:47.264
Bye, Pop.

